QuestData.Title: Time-Lost Vikings
QuestData.Description: Oi, barely made it out of that place!$B$BWe came through the portal to help, and the next thing you know, we're prisoners in the Bloodmaul Slag Mine. It was brutal! We were shackled for days, and covered in filth.$B$BAnd they took my SHIELD!
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect Olaf's Shield from the Bloodmaul Slag Mines.
